definitions.definition: A female given name from Ancient Greek . A variant of Catherine .
The 11th tropical storm of the 2005 Atlantic hurricane season, which caused catastrophic damage to Louisiana, Mississippi and parts of Alabama.
A large-scale disaster, especially one with negative political consequences.
